Rating: 1
Amy When adding noodles to soup Boiling the noodles or even cooking them with the soup makes the soup cloudy. So I 1. cook noodles seperate.. al dante . . rinse well add noodles to soup last 10 minutes( just to keep them hot)of cooking the soup. This also gets rid of the starch by cooking noodles seperately... I've made my Chicken noodle soup for 48 yrs. but with chicken breast with skin on and remove the skin and bones when cooked using a 6 or 8 Qt pot. this freezes well -Add 5 large mushrooms. . .diced finely - 1 carrot slivered finely -n- 11/2 large yellow onions . . .chopped- 4-5 green onions and tops. . .diced fine-1/2 tsp. dried sweet basil- dash of red crushed pepper-water to almost the top of the pot - salt n pepper to taste and wide noodles If watching the fat skim the fat off. I also use Kolaski noodles. or make my own. Oh, I might just submit the my recipe in a couple of days. Eneleh

