Rating: 0
Answer for Amydyson: Hi Amy, cook the soup wihout the noodles -- especially if you're leaving it on the stove for a while. Egg noodles cook very quickly and will turn mushy. Add the noodles 10-15 minutes before you're ready to eat. Enjoy!

