Rating: 4
I absolutely loved this soup. It is the best. I did make a few minor additions to the soup as well and it gave it such a delicious flavor. I added four cloves of garlic to the mushrooms while they were browning in the pan and I also added Sason Accent (used in Spanish cooking - Cuban, Puerto-Rican, etc...), Sason Accent really adds to the flavor of the soup - I used 3 packets of Sason Accent and added it to the soup. Instead of using the egg noodles I subsititued angel hair pasta and the soup was incredible. Great comfort food for the cold nights we get up here in the North.

